<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 18:19:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>雷蒙多表示，美国将于下周敲定中国车辆管制规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-finalize-chinese-vehicle-crackdown-rules-next-week-raimondo-says-2025-01-09/</link><description>美国商务部长吉娜·雷蒙多告诉路透社，即将卸任的总统乔·拜登政府计划下周敲定打击中国汽车软件和硬件的规则。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 17:43:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-finalize-chinese-vehicle-crackdown-rules-next-week-raimondo-says-2025-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>联合国预测2025年世界经济增长将保持在2.8%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/un-predicts-world-economic-growth-remain-28-2025-2025-01-09/</link><description>根据联合国周四发布的一份报告，预计 2025 年全球经济增长将保持在 2.8%，与 2024 年持平，但受到美国和中国这两个最大经济体的阻碍。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 17:38:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/un-predicts-world-economic-growth-remain-28-2025-2025-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>香港司法网站显示，开发商融创中国收到清算申请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/developer-sunac-china-gets-liquidation-petition-hong-kong-judiciary-website-2025-01-09/</link><description>香港司法机构网站周四晚间显示，负债累累的房地产开发商融创中国已收到清算申请。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 14:37:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/developer-sunac-china-gets-liquidation-petition-hong-kong-judiciary-website-2025-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>尼日利亚和中国深化安全、金融和经济增长承诺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/nigeria-china-deepen-ties-with-pledge-security-finance-economic-growth-2025-01-09/</link><description>两国外交部长周四表示，尼日利亚和中国计划深化在清洁能源、国防和金融等领域的合作，中国承诺支持尼日利亚发行熊猫债为基础设施建设提供资金。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 14:17:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/nigeria-china-deepen-ties-with-pledge-security-finance-economic-growth-2025-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>亿万富翁弗兰克·麦考特的自由计划提议竞购 TikTok 的美国资产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/billionaire-frank-mccourts-project-liberty-proposes-bid-tiktoks-us-assets-2025-01-09/</link><description>企业家、前洛杉矶道奇队老板 Frank McCourt 的 Project Liberty 及其 The People&amp;#39;s Bid 合作伙伴财团周四表示，他们提议向字节跳动正式出价收购 TikTok 的美国资产。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 14:02:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/billionaire-frank-mccourts-project-liberty-proposes-bid-tiktoks-us-assets-2025-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>维克多·欧尔班的挑战者认为欧盟和北约的牢固关系以及对俄罗斯的“务实”态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/viktor-orbans-challenger-sees-strong-eu-nato-ties-pragmatic-approach-russia-2025-01-09/</link><description>总理欧尔班·维克托的反对派挑战者彼得·马扎尔告诉路透社，如果他赢得 2026 年初的选举，他将让匈牙利坚定地留在欧盟和北约，并将努力与俄罗斯建立“务实关系”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 13:07:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/viktor-orbans-challenger-sees-strong-eu-nato-ties-pragmatic-approach-russia-2025-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国碧桂园拟削减116亿美元海外债务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-country-garden-proposes-offshore-restructuring-deal-2025-01-09/</link><description>碧桂园已向其境外债权人提出一项协议，将削减其债务116亿美元，为这家房地产开发商向香港高等法院寻求更多时间来实施重组计划铺平道路。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 11:26:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-country-garden-proposes-offshore-restructuring-deal-2025-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，Shein 计划在年中之前在伦敦首次公开募股</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-aims-london-ipo-by-mid-year-sources-say-2025-01-09/</link><description>据两位直接了解此事的消息人士透露，在线快时尚零售商 Shein 计划于今年上半年在伦敦上市，前提是该公司的首次公开募股获得监管部门的批准。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 10:18:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-aims-london-ipo-by-mid-year-sources-say-2025-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>拜登将在特朗普时代开始前推动新的俄罗斯制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-set-push-new-russia-sanctions-before-trump-era-begins-2025-01-09/</link><description>据一位美国官员称，总统乔·拜登预计将于本周公布针对俄罗斯经济的新制裁措施，作为唐纳德·特朗普上任前支持基辅对莫斯科战争努力的措施的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 10:03:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-set-push-new-russia-sanctions-before-trump-era-begins-2025-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>台海军模拟攻击演练展示钢铁实力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-navy-shows-off-its-steel-with-simulated-attack-exercise-2025-01-09/</link><description>周四，台湾海军在结束为期三天的新年演习时模拟击退敌舰，派出两艘最新、最先进的军舰率领一支舰队进入台湾海峡。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 09:15:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-navy-shows-off-its-steel-with-simulated-attack-exercise-2025-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>2025年中国电动汽车出口预计将陷入停滞</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-car-sales-extend-gains-dec-2025-01-09/</link><description>一位汽车协会官员周四表示，在2024年连续第二年蝉联出口王冠后，预计今年中国汽车出口将显着放缓，电动汽车出口预计不会出现增长。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 08:20:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-car-sales-extend-gains-dec-2025-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>由于美国利率和特朗普关税威胁仍是焦点，亚洲外汇走强</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/asian-fx-bears-firm-us-rates-trump-tariff-threats-stay-focus-2025-01-09/</link><description>路透周四的一项调查显示，由于美国今年降息幅度较小的前景继续提振美元需求，对大多数亚洲货币的看空押注攀升至数月高点，而美国潜在关税的威胁削弱了亚洲风险资产的吸引力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 07:39:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/asian-fx-bears-firm-us-rates-trump-tariff-threats-stay-focus-2025-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>上海启动外资医院试点计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/shanghai-kicks-off-plan-allow-foreign-owned-hospitals-2025-01-09/</link><description>上海启动了一项计划，允许在中国重点经济区、生物制药区和外籍人口较多的中心城区设立外商独资医院。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 06:54:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/shanghai-kicks-off-plan-allow-foreign-owned-hospitals-2025-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国发现MPOX新菌株群</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-discovers-cluster-new-mpox-strain-2025-01-09/</link><description>中国卫生部门周四表示，去年世界卫生组织宣布全球公共卫生紧急状态后，随着病毒感染蔓延到更多国家，他们发现了新的突变型MPOX菌株Ib。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 05:58:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/china-discovers-cluster-new-mpox-strain-2025-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>由于需求疲软，2024年中国消费者价格将停滞</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-consumer-inflation-slows-dec-2025-01-09/</link><description>受国内需求持续疲弱的影响，出厂价格连续第二年下跌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 01:45:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-consumer-inflation-slows-dec-2025-01-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>